Venga, siéntese.

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:29.030
Despacio.

00:11:29.030 --> 00:11:29.600
Abuela.

00:11:30.890 --> 00:11:31.620
No se enfade.

00:11:32.810 --> 00:11:33.380
Xiaoxi.

